description: Let me introduce another dude totally fed up with his job. He studied to be a car mechanic because cars were his big hobby. Once he finished school and started working, he found out it wasn't so great. He asked me to find him anything else, ideally a job involving computers and people. It wasn't easy but I managed to get him a position at an IT company. The guy was really happy about it until I told him about the mediation fee he would have to pay. He was in a tough situation. All his relatives were dead, he had no siblings, had no girlfriend... I truly felt sorry for the guy. Don't worry, I had something for him. I just wanted to play with him, maybe even make him feel better. I guess, I was a bit sentimental today... or maybe just horny.
title: Dirty Scout 223
